---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Services | PIVOT Management Consultants" description="Training and consulting that deliver results. Lean, Six Sigma, TRIZ, Quality Systems, and operational excellence.">
  <section class="py-12 sm:py-16 border-b border-border">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <h1 class="text-[1.75rem] sm:text-[2rem] lg:text-[2.25rem] text-ink mb-2">
        Operational intervention — not training.
      </h1>
      <p class="text-sm sm:text-base text-ink-light max-w-2xl">
        Every engagement is measured against your P&L. We embed until the numbers move and your team owns the capability.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Consulting -->
  <section class="py-12 sm:py-16">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <h2 class="text-lg sm:text-xl mb-2">Consulting</h2>
      <p class="text-sm text-ink-light mb-6 max-w-2xl">We diagnose challenges, align teams, and deliver measurable outcomes across four key areas.</p>
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-5">
        <div class="rounded-lg p-6 bg-surface-alt border border-border">
          <h3 class="font-heading text-lg font-bold text-ink mb-2">Operations</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-ink-light mb-3">Lean methodology, Six Sigma implementation, and TRIZ application for process improvement.</p>
          <ul class="text-sm text-ink-muted space-y-1">
            <li>- Value stream mapping & line redesign</li>
            <li>- Cycle time & throughput improvement</li>
            <li>- TRIZ-based constraint dissolution</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="rounded-lg p-6 bg-surface-alt border border-border">
          <h3 class="font-heading text-lg font-bold text-ink mb-2">Quality Systems</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-ink-light mb-3">ISO system setup, QMS simplification, auditing, corrective action, supplier auditing, and complaint response.</p>
          <ul class="text-sm text-ink-muted space-y-1">
            <li>- ISO 9001 / 13485 / AS9100 readiness</li>
            <li>- CAPA process optimisation</li>
            <li>- Feedback monitoring & supplier auditing</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="rounded-lg p-6 bg-surface-alt border border-border">
          <h3 class="font-heading text-lg font-bold text-ink mb-2">Risk & Compliance</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-ink-light mb-3">Risk management, supplier management systems, and cybersecurity integration.</p>
          <ul class="text-sm text-ink-muted space-y-1">
            <li>- Enterprise risk frameworks</li>
            <li>- Supplier management systems</li>
            <li>- Cybersecurity & compliance integration</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="rounded-lg p-6 bg-surface-alt border border-border">
          <h3 class="font-heading text-lg font-bold text-ink mb-2">Innovation</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-ink-light mb-3">TRIZ-driven product and process innovation. Break contradictions your R&D team has accepted as trade-offs.</p>
          <ul class="text-sm text-ink-muted space-y-1">
            <li>- Inventive problem-solving workshops</li>
            <li>- Contradiction analysis & resolution</li>
            <li>- Technology roadmap development</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Two-phase methodology -->
  <section class="py-10 sm:py-14 bg-surface-alt border-y border-border">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <h2 class="text-lg sm:text-xl mb-5">How we engage</h2>
      <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
        <div class="bg-surface rounded-lg p-5 border border-border">
          <p class="text-sm font-semibold text-ink mb-1">Phase 1: Assessment & Planning</p>
          <p class="text-xs text-ink-light">We gain an in-depth understanding of your business operations, identify opportunities for improvement, and determine alignment with strategy.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-surface rounded-lg p-5 border border-border">
          <p class="text-sm font-semibold text-ink mb-1">Phase 2: Results Delivery</p>
          <p class="text-xs text-ink-light">We design and deploy improvement strategies, delivering quick results while institutionalising long-term improvement efforts.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Training -->
  <section class="py-12 sm:py-16">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <h2 class="text-lg sm:text-xl mb-2">Training</h2>
      <p class="text-sm text-ink-light mb-6 max-w-2xl">All training requires completion of real projects to ensure knowledge retention, employee empowerment, and a clear return on investment.</p>
      <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-3 gap-4">
        <div class="rounded-lg p-5 bg-surface-alt border border-border">
          <p class="text-sm font-semibold text-ink mb-1">On-Site</p>
          <p class="text-xs text-ink-light">Hands-on facilitation at your workplace. Consultants work alongside teams for real-time concept application.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="rounded-lg p-5 bg-surface-alt border border-border">
          <p class="text-sm font-semibold text-ink mb-1">Remote</p>
          <p class="text-xs text-ink-light">Interactive virtual sessions with digital collaboration tools and practical assignments. No travel costs.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="rounded-lg p-5 bg-surface-alt border border-border">
          <p class="text-sm font-semibold text-ink mb-1">Lunch & Learn</p>
          <p class="text-xs text-ink-light">Short-format sessions introducing essential concepts and tools. Ideal for building awareness and inspiring teams.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
